exp.libs.utils.io

Class SerialFlowWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • exp.libs.utils.io.SerialFlowWriter

  • public class SerialFlowWriter
extends Object
     批量序列化写入器(需配合读取器使用).
        用于把多个内存对象写到外存的同一个序列化文件.
 
 使用示例:
        SerialFlowWriter sfw = new SerialFlowWriter(FILE_PATH, true);
        while(true) {
                sfw.write(obj);
                // .....
        }
        sfw.flush();
 
        sfw.write(obj2);
        sfw.write(obj3);
        sfw.close();

    PROJECT : exp-libs
    SUPPORT : https://exp-blog.com
    Since:
    JDK 1.8+
    Version:
    2022-03-06
    Author:
    EXP: exp.lqb@foxmail.com
